{"body": [{"indent": 0, "text": ["Camera"], "type": "title", "extent": [0, 11], "level": 0}, {"indent": 0, "type": "summary", "extent": [54, 165], "text": ["Adds a camera to the scene. You can Ctrl-click the shelf tool to create a camera from the current view."]}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [215, 479], "text": ["There are three ways you can place cameras in the ", {"text": ["scene view"], "fullpath": "/ref/views/3dview", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/ref/views/3dview"}, ". They can be moved once they are placed by either dragging them in the ", {"text": ["scene view"], "fullpath": "/ref/views/3dview", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/ref/views/3dview"}, " or changing the values in the ", {"text": ["parameter editor"], "fullpath": "/ref/panes/parms", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/ref/panes/parms"}, "."]}, {"body": [{"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 8, "blevel": 10, "type": "ord", "extent": [550, 650], "text": ["Click the desired ", {"text": ["camera"], "fullpath": "/nodes/obj/cam", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/obj/cam"}, " from the ", {"text": ["Lights and Cameras"], "type": "ui"}, " tab."]}, {"body": [{"indent": 12, "type": "para", "extent": [731, 830], "text": ["You can hold ", {"keys": ["Alt"], "text": null, "type": "keys"}, " to detach the shape from the construction plane."]}], "indent": 8, "text": ["Move the cursor into the ", {"text": ["scene view"], "fullpath": "/ref/views/3dview", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/ref/views/3dview"}, ". "], "extent": [650, 731], "container": true, "blevel": 10, "type": "ord"}, {"indent": 8, "blevel": 10, "type": "ord", "extent": [830, 928], "text": ["Click ", {"keys": ["LMB"], "text": null, "type": "keys"}, " to place the camera anywhere in the ", {"text": ["scene view"], "fullpath": "/ref/views/3dview", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/ref/views/3dview"}, ". "]}], "container": true, "type": "ord_group"}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Place cameras in a specific location in the scene view"], "role": "item", "extent": [479, 550], "container": true, "type": "task"}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 8, "blevel": 10, "type": "ord", "extent": [972, 1072], "text": ["Click the desired ", {"text": ["camera"], "fullpath": "/nodes/obj/cam", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/obj/cam"}, " from the ", {"text": ["Lights and Cameras"], "type": "ui"}, " tab."]}, {"indent": 8, "blevel": 10, "type": "ord", "extent": [1072, 1198], "text": ["Move your cursor into the ", {"text": ["scene view"], "fullpath": "/ref/views/3dview", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/ref/views/3dview"}, " and press ", {"keys": ["Enter"], "text": null, "type": "keys"}, " to place the shape at the origin."]}], "container": true, "type": "ord_group"}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Place cameras at the origin"], "role": "item", "extent": [928, 972], "container": true, "type": "task"}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 8, "blevel": 10, "type": "ord", "extent": [1251, 1360], "text": [{"keys": ["Ctrl"], "text": null, "type": "keys"}, " click the desired ", {"text": ["camera"], "fullpath": "/nodes/obj/cam", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/obj/cam"}, " from the ", {"text": ["Lights and Cameras"], "type": "ui"}, " tab."]}, {"indent": 8, "blevel": 10, "type": "ord", "extent": [1360, 1558], "text": ["Use the handles or edit the values in the ", {"text": ["parameter editor"], "fullpath": "/ref/panes/parms", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/ref/panes/parms"}, " to move the ", {"text": ["camera"], "fullpath": "/nodes/obj/cam", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/obj/cam"}, " to the desired location in the ", {"text": ["scene view"], "fullpath": "/ref/views/3dview", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/ref/views/3dview"}, "."]}], "container": true, "type": "ord_group"}, {"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [1558, 1717], "text": ["When looking through the camera there are handles on the sides of the ", {"text": ["scene view"], "fullpath": "/ref/views/3dview", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/ref/views/3dview"}, " which allows you to orient and crop."]}, {"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [1717, 1778], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/images/shelf/lightsandcameras_view.png", "scheme": "Image", "type": "link", "value": "/images/shelf/lightsandcameras_view.png"}]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Place a camera by looking through it"], "role": "item", "extent": [1198, 1251], "container": true, "type": "task"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group", "type": "task_group"}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [1798, 2043], "text": ["Clicking ", {"keys": ["RMB"], "text": null, "type": "keys"}, " on cameras in the ", {"text": ["scene view"], "fullpath": "/ref/views/3dview", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/ref/views/3dview"}, " gives you more ", {"text": ["camera and light manipulator handle options"], "fullpath": "/basics/handles", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/basics/handles"}, ". The two that are unique to cameras are the focus handle and the frustum handle."]}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [2063, 2153], "text": ["Allows you to set the near and far clipping planes and the focal length."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Frustum handle"], "extent": [2043, 2063], "container": true, "type": "dt"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [2171, 2231], "text": ["Allows you to control the depth map focus."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Focus handle"], "extent": [2153, 2171], "container": true, "type": "dt"}], "container": true, "type": "dt_group"}], "indent": 4, "level": 3, "text": ["Handles"], "extent": [1778, 1798], "container": true, "type": "h", "id": null}, {"body": [{"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [2461, 2519], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/images/ui/viewport_menus_anno.png", "scheme": "Image", "type": "link", "value": "../images/ui/viewport_menus_anno.png"}]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Look through a ", {"text": ["camera"], "fullpath": "/nodes/obj/cam", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/obj/cam"}, " as described above. You can also choose a camera to look through once it is created by choosing it in the ", {"text": ["camera menu"], "fullpath": "/basics/view", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/basics/view"}, ". "], "extent": [2278, 2461], "container": true, "blevel": 6, "type": "ord"}, {"indent": 4, "blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "extent": [2519, 2830], "text": ["Lock the ", {"text": ["camera"], "fullpath": "/nodes/obj/cam", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/obj/cam"}, " to the view by clicking the ", {"text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/VIEW/display_lock_camera", "scheme": "Icon", "type": "link", "value": "VIEW/display_lock_camera"}, " Lock camera/light to the view button, which is located on the toolbar on the right side of the view. You can also lock the camera to view by by turning on ", {"text": ["Tie Camera (or Light) to View"], "type": "ui"}, " in the camera menu."]}, {"indent": 4, "blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "extent": [2830, 2929], "text": ["Use the ", {"text": ["tumble, track, and dolly"], "fullpath": "/basics/view", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/basics/view"}, " keys to move the ", {"text": ["camera"], "fullpath": "/nodes/obj/cam", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/obj/cam"}, "."]}, {"indent": 4, "blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "extent": [2929, 2971], "text": ["Unlock the camera to place it."]}], "container": true, "type": "ord_group"}], "indent": 4, "level": 3, "text": ["Use the view keys to move a camera"], "extent": [2231, 2278], "container": true, "type": "h", "id": null}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 4, "blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "extent": [3015, 3049], "text": ["Create an object."]}, {"indent": 4, "blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "extent": [3049, 3092], "text": ["Create a ", {"text": ["camera"], "fullpath": "/nodes/obj/cam", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/obj/cam"}, "."]}, {"indent": 4, "blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "extent": [3092, 3158], "text": ["Click ", {"text": ["Look At"], "type": "ui"}, " on the ", {"text": ["Modify shelf"], "fullpath": "/shelf/modify", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/shelf/modify"}, "."]}, {"indent": 4, "blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "extent": [3158, 3219], "text": ["Select the object to look at and press ", {"keys": ["Enter"], "text": null, "type": "keys"}, "."]}], "container": true, "type": "ord_group"}, {"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [3219, 3386], "text": ["You can also make a camera look at an object by setting it on the ", {"text": ["Lookat Options"], "type": "ui"}, " tab on the ", {"text": ["Transform tab"], "type": "ui"}, " of the ", {"text": ["parameter editor"], "fullpath": "/ref/panes/parms", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/ref/panes/parms"}, "."]}], "indent": 4, "level": 3, "text": ["Make a camera look at an object"], "extent": [2971, 3015], "container": true, "type": "h", "id": null}], "indent": 0, "level": 2, "text": ["Placing cameras in the viewer"], "extent": [165, 215], "container": true, "type": "h", "id": "includeme"}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [3395, 3427], "text": [{"text": ["Switcher"], "fullpath": "/nodes/obj/switcher", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/obj/switcher"}]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [3427, 3471], "text": [{"text": ["Stereo Camera Rig"], "fullpath": "/nodes/obj/stereocamrig", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/obj/stereocamrig"}]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [3471, 3500], "text": [{"text": ["VR Camera"], "fullpath": "/nodes/obj/vrcam", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/obj/vrcam"}]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [3500, 3527], "text": [{"text": ["Look At"], "fullpath": "/shelf/lookat", "scheme": null, "type":